-- BP Advances on Investors' Expectations Dudley Will Replace Hayward as CEO
-- Will Kennedy
-- 2010-07-26T07:04:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-26/bp-advances-on-investors-expectations-dudley-will-replace-hayward-as-ceo.html

          
          
             BP Plc rose as much as 3 percent in
London trading on expectations Robert Dudley will be announced
as successor to Chief Executive Officer Tony Hayward tomorrow.  
          
          


  


        